nodes.text: Jamie Alcroft (born January 18, 1949)[source?] is an American comedian and voice actor who voiced Sio Bibble, AT-PT drivers, and Javelin submarine captains in Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds and voiced Shai, Jalta, Gavon Kroan, as well as additional voices for Star Wars: The Old Republic.
